Class CommandStrategyProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.fineract.batch.command.CommandStrategyProvider

  • @Component
public class CommandStrategyProvider
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides an appropriate CommandStrategy using the 'method' and 'resourceUrl'. CommandStrategy bean is created using Spring Application Context.
